'''Aɣrda n Bariz''' (s yism nns anṣli s [[Tutlayt Tanglizt|tnglizt]] : Ratatouille) iga yan lfilm tskrt carika n [[Pixar]] d [[Wald Disney Pictures]]. Ɣwad aygan ufilm wis tam ad tsfɣ [[Pixar]], yura tt d ibidd f usufɣ nns ssi [[Brad Bird]]. Iffuɣ d ufilm ad ɣ ammas n tidaliwin n sinima ɣ usggwas n 2007.

Afilm ad ar isawal f lqist n yan [[Aɣrda|uɣrda]], iga s yism Kzmin. Ikka-tt-inn izdɣ ɣ yan udwar ɣ tmazirt n [[Fransa]] ntta d tawja nns imqqurn nna ɣ llan tugt n iɣrdayn yaḍn. Mac ran laqdar ad disn ingiri iftu s ammas n tmdint n [[Bariz]]. Ɣin aɣ imaqqar d yan ufrux iɣama dis ɣ [[Tigmmi|tgmmi]] nns ar t ittaws ula ɣ twuri nns ɣ ammas n unwal n yan resto bahra ittawssan ɣ tuẓẓumt n [[Bariz]].
